      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p>Baking out textures involves two easy steps.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"31034aec-2c51-4c5d-9c2e-e3924ab7487b\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p><span class=\"confluence-link\">See <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19662127/Baking\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19662127\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Baking</a> for more information.</span></p></div></div><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-note conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"d1227057-b931-435b-bbd4-85845da8ef42\" data-macro-name=\"note\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>The user should supply UVs (UV mapped) for the object to be baked.</p></div></div><h3 id=\"Baking-SetBakeHider\">Set Bake Hider</h3><p>Instead of using raytrace, set it to<strong> bake</strong>.</p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" width=\"650\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645511/bakehider.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433142248&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=650&amp;height=462\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645511/bakehider.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433142248&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544645533\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"bakehider.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544645511\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"c900891e-80d7-48a8-888e-f5f91218e7b8\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645511/bakehider.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433142248&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=868&amp;height=617 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645511/bakehider.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433142248&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=650&amp;height=462 1x\"></span></p><p><br/></p><h3 id=\"Baking-AddPxrBakeTexture\">Add PxrBakeTexture</h3><p>In your RIS Network, add a <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661581/PxrBakeTexture\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661581\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">PxrBakeTexture</a> VOP.  Wire its output to a PxrSurface color parameter so it will get evaluated.</p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" width=\"650\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645511/pxrbake.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433142248&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=650&amp;height=301\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645511/pxrbake.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433142248&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544645527\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrbake.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544645511\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"0e262c41-c06b-4f55-8cac-7d4f9382f50e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645511/pxrbake.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433142248&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=655&amp;height=304 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645511/pxrbake.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433142248&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=650&amp;height=301 1x\"></span></p><p>In the PxrBakeTexture VOP, set its output FileName.  See <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661581/PxrBakeTexture\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661581\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">PxrBakeTexture</a> for descriptions of each parameter.</p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" width=\"650\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645511/pxrbaketexture.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433142248&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=650&amp;height=267\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645511/pxrbaketexture.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433142248&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544645530\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrbaketexture.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544645511\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"c3e08f34-0992-4682-b376-cf247f335d8c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645511/pxrbaketexture.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433142248&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=808&amp;height=333 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645511/pxrbaketexture.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433142248&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=650&amp;height=267 1x\"></span></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>"
    }
